{"tid":2361211,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉淑儀：許智峯潛逃 可透過國際刑警發通緝令","createTime":"2021-01-10T12:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T13:50:32.000Z","uid":230530,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"480b7e9e261cb5aba8d63a2b774003145bf0de62","tid":2361211,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"許智峯潛逃 可透過國際刑警發通緝令<br />\n<br />\n至於我積極敦促特區政府跟進許智峯棄保潛逃案，要求引渡2名涉事的丹麥國會議員，特區政府可以通過《刑事司法互助協議》，要求當地執法部門協助落口供，因為有關議員涉嫌協助、教唆他人犯罪，即使在境外串謀都同屬犯罪，當然最終丹麥方面會否答應是另一回事，但至少港府應先盡自身責任。香港是國際刑警成員，只要有足夠證據，我認為當然可以透過國際刑警發通緝令，將相關人士緝拿到港歸案，捍衞香港的尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n節目重溫連結：<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/ontherecord\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fontherecord&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7YT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=fb8c2910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/ontherecord</a>"},{"pid":"fe1b29f68026c76349c5095e6aaa8855532b68ac","tid":2361211,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266e8fd9274a050bea33dbf7bc2ac249c1232578","tid":2361211,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"【協助許智峯潛逃的丹麥議員 或已最少觸犯兩項罪行】<br />\n<br />\n自從我於1月6日在立法會作出書面提問，指兩名丹麥左翼綠黨議員 Uffe Elbaek 及保守黨 Katarina Ammitzb&oslash;ll 於去年發出虛假邀請，聲稱舉行環保會議，協助前立法會議員許智峯潛逃，掩飾其流亡目的，他們是否已觸犯《刑事訴訟程序條例》第 89 條中「任何人協助，教唆，慫使或促使另一人犯罪，屬同一罪行有罪。」呢？我認為兩名協助許智峯潛逃的丹麥議員，或已最少觸犯兩項罪行，包括《刑事訴訟程序條例》（第221章）第89條，任何人協助、教唆、慫使或促致另一人犯任何罪行，即屬就同一罪行有罪。另外亦有機會觸犯《刑事罪行條例》（第200章）第159A條的串謀罪。其中港府對串謀罪有域外管轄權，若嫌疑人日後進入香港境內，執法部門可作拘捕。"},{"pid":"ef3cc7a404438ce7ae3eca6c1a1d2698f72cc759","tid":2361211,"uid":287422,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做正契弟，你睇你做完外國仲會唔會同你繼續司法互助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4b3e5b58fb6207df3eadb08636246b53a80870","tid":2361211,"uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ef3cc7a404438ce7ae3eca6c1a1d2698f72cc759","tid":2361211,"uid":287422,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做正契弟，你睇你做完外國仲會唔會同你繼續司法互助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"一早無左啦"},{"pid":"6785e1fad87abd335481d507ad7a371ca30b4e85","tid":2361211,"uid":85586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"姐姐係咪諗住靠今鋪升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8edd7d77474d07d3aa62b99c8b3491454c1039","tid":2361211,"uid":50931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"隻人型豬個女幾時番大灣區"},{"pid":"9a36f1fc83125e124e189e1c35c850b63d068eb3","tid":2361211,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":