":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef3cc7a404438ce7ae3eca6c1a1d2698f72cc759","tid":2361211,"uid":287422,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做正契弟，你睇你做完外國仲會唔會同你繼續司法互助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"//香港是國際刑警成員，只要有足夠證據，我認為當然可以透過國際刑警發通緝令，將相關人士緝拿到港歸案，捍衞香港的尊嚴。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇吓國際刑警點講所謂嘅Red Notice「紅色通緝令」嘅實質功能先啦<br />\n<blockquote>Are the individuals wanted by INTERPOL?<br />\n<br />\nNo, they are wanted by a country or an international tribunal. <strong><span class=\"red\">INTERPOL cannot compel the law enforcement authorities in any country to arrest someone who is the subject of a Red Notice</span></strong>. <br />\nEach member country decides what legal value it gives to a Red Notice and the authority of their law enforcement officers to make arrests.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.interpol.int/How-we-work/Notices/Red-Notices\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interpol.int%2FHow-we-work%2FNotices%2FRed-Notices&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7YT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=073df4ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.interpol.int/How-we-work/Notices/Red-Notices</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係準確嚟講 國際刑警果啲唔係叫「通緝令」啊 <br />\n果張嘢只係份文件通知各成員國有其中一個成員國需要緝拿某一個人當中係毫無實質法律效力 <br />\n最終拘捕同引渡與否都係基建於國家同國家之間嘅引渡協議 依家香港同西方國家無撚晒引渡協議 你出幾多張通緝令都係廢架囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb43570aa6fcf802346b424c31b1fca163de44f","tid":2361211,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3cab9d053300a4c3918fc3d555eaae4cac3184","tid":2361211,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef3cc7a404438ce7ae3eca6c1a1d2698f72cc759","tid":2361211,"uid":287422,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做正契弟，你睇你做完外國仲會唔會同你繼續司法互助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"//香港是國際刑警成員，只要有足夠證據，我認為當然可以透過國際刑警發通緝令，將相關人士緝拿到港歸案，捍衞香港的尊嚴。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇吓國際刑警點講所謂嘅Red Notice「紅色通緝令」嘅實質功能先啦<br />\n<blockquote>Are the individuals wanted by INTERPOL?<br />\n<br />\nNo, they are wanted by a country or an international tribunal. <strong><span class=\"red\">INTERPOL cannot compel the law enforcement authorities in any country to arrest someone who is the subject of a Red Notice</span></strong>. <br />\nEach member country decides what legal value it gives to a Red Notice and the authority of their law enforcement officers to make arrests.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.interpol.int/How-we-work/Notices/Red-Notices\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interpol.int%2FHow-we-work%2FNotices%2FRed-Notices&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7YT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=073df4ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.interpol.int/How-we-work/Notices/Red-Notices</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係準確嚟講 國際刑警果啲唔係叫「通緝令」啊 <br />\n果張嘢只係份文件通知各成員國有其中一個成員國需要緝拿某一個人當中係毫無實質法律效力 <br />\n最終拘捕同引渡與否都係基建於國家同國家之間嘅引渡協議 依家香港同西方國家無撚晒引渡協議 你出幾多張通緝令都係廢架囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"好難講， 今年唔同上年了<br />\n今日無，聽日可能會有返引渡協議"},{"pid":"b351d25fd95bdab443684fee1ace28a65a318a70","tid":2361211,"uid":303895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:04:26.000Z","msg":"派出三萬 雖遠必豬"},{"pid":"d918693e09bb4c7ae59e7152f118b23f32565ad2","tid":2361211,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3cab9d053300a4c3918fc3d555eaae4cac3184","tid":2361211,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef3cc7a404438ce7ae3eca6c1a1d2698f72cc759","tid":2361211,"uid":287422,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做正契弟，你睇你做完外國仲會唔會同你繼續司法互助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"//香港是國際刑警成員，只要有足夠證據，我認為當然可以透過國際刑警發通緝令，將相關人士緝拿到港歸案，捍衞香港的尊嚴。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇吓國際刑警點講所謂嘅Red Notice「紅色通緝令」嘅實質功能先啦<br />\n<blockquote>Are the individuals wanted by INTERPOL?<br />\n<br />\nNo, they are wanted by a country or an international tribunal. <strong><span class=\"red\">INTERPOL cannot compel the law enforcement authorities in any country to arrest someone who is the subject of a Red Notice</span></strong>. <br />\nEach member country decides what legal value it gives to a Red Notice and the authority of their law enforcement officers to make arrests.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.interpol.int/How-we-work/Notices/Red-Notices\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interpol.int%2FHow-we-work%2FNotices%2FRed-Notices&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7YT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=073df4ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.interpol.int/How-we-work/Notices/Red-Notices</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係準確嚟講 國際刑警果啲唔係叫「通緝令」啊 <br />\n果張嘢只係份文件通知各成員國有其中一個成員國需要緝拿某一個人當中係毫無實質法律效力 <br />\n最終拘捕同引渡與否都係基建於國家同國家之間嘅引渡協議 依家香港同西方國家無撚晒引渡協議 你出幾多張通緝令都係廢架囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"香港同歐美簽嘅逃犯引渡協議都會有呢段架啦<br />\n<blockquote>//<strong><ins>Mandatory Refusal to Surrender</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">A fugitive offender shall not be surrendered if the Requested Party considers that the offence of which that person is accused or</span></strong> <strong><span class=\"red\">was convicted is a political offence</span></strong> or an offence of a political character.//</blockquote><br />\n根本歐美國家批得政治庇護俾你想拉嘅人喺當地居留 就證明咗人地決定咗你個控罪係政治檢控嚟 你個所謂引渡要求就必然俾人地拒絕啦 <br />\n<br />\n孽瘤真係以為個個都好似佢咁明知柒硬都仲係要仆咗出嚟獻世咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bea7aa7de58ca7b9d04229d6216ce041cabff50","tid":2361211,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcb43570aa6fcf802346b424c31b1fca163de44f","tid":2361211,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3cab9d053300a4c3918fc3d555eaae4cac3184","tid":2361211,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quo